data.description: Welcome to your dream home on a serene cul-de-sac in the heart of Annapolis! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of tranquility and convenience, located just minutes away from downtown Annapolis and a host of amenities.  🌟 Key Features: ✅ Spacious 3 Bedrooms ✅ Open-concept Living & Dining Areas ✅ Cozy Fireplace for Those Chilly Nights ✅ Private Deck for Relaxing & Entertaining ✅ Quiet, Family-Friendly Cul-de-sac ✅ Proximity to Downtown Annapolis & Amenities  This home exudes charm and is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open living and dining areas are perfect for gatherings, and the well-appointed kitchen will delight any chef. Enjoy the cozy fireplace in the spacious living room on those cooler evenings. Located in a peaceful cul-de-sac, you'll have privacy and minimal traffic. But when it's time for shopping, dining, or exploring downtown Annapolis, you're just a short drive away. You'll also find a variety of amenities, parks, and schools within easy reach.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your forever home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the best of Annapolis living!
